name: Lead To Opportunity
query:
SELECT 
    COUNT(leads.name) AS lead_count,
    (COUNT(leads.name) * 100.0 / total_leads.total_count) AS lead_percentage
FROM 
    `tabLead` as leads
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT COUNT(*) AS total_count
    FROM `tabLead`
) AS total_leads ON 1=1
WHERE 
    leads.status = 'Lead';
